3. cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) - The paper may be relevant to social networks if the broadcast channel is used for communication between individuals or groups. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper may be relevant to multimedia communication if the broadcast channel is used for transmitting audio or video content. 
5. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper may be relevant to systems and control if the feedback is used to control the transmission of information in the channel.
